data.description: Welcome to your new home! This meticulously maintained home is a true gem, boasting a spacious floor plan and high-end finishes throughout. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by an inviting foyer that sets the tone for the rest of the home. The living area is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The cozy fireplace is perfect for the cold Missouri winters. Gleaming hardwood floors lead you through the open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the living room to the kitchen. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing a family meal, this kitchen is both stylish and functional. The master suite is a private retreat, offering a serene space to unwind after a long day. The en-suite bathroom is spa-like, complete with a walk in shower, large vanity, and lots of privacy. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and perfect for a growing family or accommodating guests. Step outside to discover a beautifully landscaped backyard oasis. The patio provides an ideal setting for al fresco dining or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. The well-manicured lawn offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and recreation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home - a place where timeless elegance meets modern living.
